+ Left and right ARROW keys will be reserved for the rotation of the FOV
+ W,A,S,D will be reserved for moving the point through the map
+ ESC and the red cross Will close the window
+ The map will only contain these characters N, S , E , W , 0 , 1
  => N: The player will be facing NORTH
  => S: The player will be facing SOUTH
  => E: The player will be facing EAST
  => W: The player will be facing WEST
  => 0: An empty space
  => 1: A wall

+ The game should have a map content validator and elements validator.
+ The game informations can be separated by one or more spaces.
+ The map content should always be the last thin the file.
